    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear and tear from years of faithful service, it remains a solid and functional choice for anyone needing reliable transportation. It's a great opportunity to own a capable car at a fantastic price point\u2014perfect for a commuter or a first-time driver!",
